<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - Reservaloo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/Logo.png">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/stylesheets/error.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="error-container">
        <div class="card shadow-lg error-card">
            <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle error-icon"></i>
                </div>
                <h1 class="card-title text-danger mb-3">{{message}}</h1>
                {{#if error.status}}
                <h4 class="card-subtitle mb-3 text-muted">Código de error: {{error.status}}</h4>
                {{/if}}
                <p class="mt-3 mb-4">Ha ocurrido un problema. Por favor, vuelve a intentarlo más tarde o contacta al administrador.</p>
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg px-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Volver al login
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
